This paper discusses measures for characterizing the complexity of classification problems, which is a topic that is relevant to several sub-fields of computer science. However, given the focus on machine learning and pattern recognition, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning). Other likely sub-categories include cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.CV (Computer Vision), cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
